Vim:

FILE:
run vim ==  shell $vim project_name.c
-command mode: use commands )default when vim opened
-session mode: insert text
switch to session mode == i
switch to command mode == Esc
quit vim == :q
save file == :w
open another file == :e name_of_file

EDIT:
ir al final de una linea == $
ir al principio de una linea == ^
buscar algo en el archivo == ctrl+S cosa_que_busco
reedit file == :e_name_of_file.c

BUFFERS:
split screen vertically (linea vertical) == :vs
split screen horizontally (linea horizontal) == :sp
move between buffers == ctrl+W arrows
close buffer == :q

42 HEADER:
:Stdhe

